<h1>Architecture</h1>
<pre class="bg-light p-3 rounded">
FilmStudio.Web (Blazor Server)
    │  REST + SignalR
    ▼
FilmStudio.Api  (:5088)
    │  JobHub  ·  FilmJobService
    ▼
FilmStudio.Engine (native C# — no Python)
    · Book prepare (PdfPig + page render + Grok vision)
    · Stage 1 (Grok chat) / Stage 2 (planner)
    · Characters (Grok image) · multi-ref video
    · FFmpeg remux/WIP (progress over SignalR)
    · Review / edit log · cost ledger
    · writes assets/video/scene_XX_clip_YY.mp4
</pre>
